&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Complaints Manager - Band 7&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for a motivated and proactive individual to join the Patient Experience team as a Complaints Manager at the Royal United Hospitals, Bath. &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The postholder will be responsible for leading the complaints process in line with national legislation in responding to and learning from complaints. Intially the post is fixed term for 12 months due to the secondment of the previous postholder.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt; &lt;strong&gt;You will be supported by the Lead for Patient and Carer Experience and be part of a friendly and inclusive team&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;





&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
